    "intro": "This document standardises how Sales Orders, repeat jobs, and new opportunities are captured and prepared before entering production. It provides a structured pipeline for Merchandising to gather information, validate requirements, and ensure every job is ready for a clean handover into the Job Intake process. The aim is to improve consistency, visibility, and operational control ahead of production scheduling.",
